# ☀ Solaire - A GitHub Repository Template

`Solaire` is a "readme" repository (shows a banner on user's main page), as well as a template repository which can be used to quickly spawn new repositories.

## Rationale

Add rationale here

---
## Structure

```bash
$ tree
./
├─ README.md/                   # This readme template.
├─ CHANGELOG.md/                # List of versions and changes.
├─ CONTRIBUTING.md/             # Contributing guide (getting started, issues, PRs, etc.)
├─ DEVELOPMENT.md/              # Technical development guidelines (coe style, tools, testing, etc.)
├─ .gitignore/                  # List of default ignore files/directories.
├─ .github/                     # Contains github repository configuration.
│  ├─ ISSUE_TEMPLATE/           # GitHub issue templates.
│  │  ├─ bug_report.md          # Bug report template.
│  │  ├─ feature_request.md     # New feature template.
```

